            <form>
               <orth>[church building]</orth>
            </form>
            <def>(Old churches never had back rooms; generally there was just a small entry-way and then the church proper; in Protestant Churches there was no centre aisle.) <graphic url="CanadaMacKinnonetalecclesillust1.jpg" width="300px"/>
